<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>웹 취약점 실습 메인 페이지</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      padding: 40px;
      background: #000;
      color: #0f0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      position: relative;
    }
    .top-button {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      left: 20px;
    }
    .top-button a {
      color: #0f0;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .top-button a:hover {
      color: #fff;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #0f0;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .menu {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 15px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
    }
    .menu a {
      padding: 10px 15px;
      background: #000;
      color: #0f0;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid #fff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }
    .menu a:hover {
      background: #111;
      color: #0f0;
    }
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 10px;
      right: 20px;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .welcome {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #0f0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="top-button">
    <a href="/">🏠</a>
  </div>

  <h1>웹 취약점 실습 메인 페이지</h1>

  <% if (user) { %>
    <div class="welcome">
      환영합니다, <%= user.userid %>님!
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="menu">
    <% if (user) { %>
      <a href="/board">게시판 (Stored XSS)</a>
      <a href="/upload">파일 업로드 (Webshell)</a>

      <% if (user) { %>
        <!-- 관리자 전용 메뉴 -->
        <a href="/profile/<%= user.id %>">프로필</a>
      <% } %>

      <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/register">회원가입</a>
      <a href="/login">로그인</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">시큐리티아카데미5기 (김선우 김동민 서상현)</div>
</body>
</html>
